-- =========================================
-- Data Quality & NULL Value Notes
-- =========================================

/*
Table: customers
Column: phone

Issue:
1,267 NULL values out of 1,445 rows.

Analysis:
Missing phone numbers are expected because
not every customer provided a phone number.

Action:
No action required since the column
is already defined as NULLable.
*/

/*
Table: orders
Column: shipped_date

Issue:
170 NULL values found.

Analysis:
NULL shipped dates indicate orders
that have not yet been shipped.

Action:
No action required.
*/

/*
Table: staffs
Column: manager_id

Issue:
1 NULL value found.

Analysis:
The NULL value belongs to the top-level
manager who does not report to anyone.

Action:
No action required.
*/
